affixes.name: Fortified
affixes.description: Non-boss enemies have 20% more health and inflict up to 30% increased damage.

affixes.name: Bolstering
affixes.description: When any non-boss enemy dies, its death cry empowers nearby allies, temporarily increasing their maximum health by 15% and damage by 20%.

affixes.name: Storming
affixes.description: While in combat, enemies periodically summon damaging whirlwinds.

affixes.name: Thundering
affixes.description: Enemies have 5% more health. While in combat, players are periodically overcharged with primal power from Raszageth's unending storm. This power comes with great risk, and failure to discharge it quickly can have stunning consequences.

affixes.name: Tyrannical
affixes.description: Bosses have 30% more health. Bosses and their minions inflict up to 15% increased damage.

affixes.name: Sanguine
affixes.description: When slain, non-boss enemies leave behind a lingering pool of ichor that heals their allies and damages players.

affixes.name: Explosive
affixes.description: While in combat, enemies periodically summon Explosive Orbs that will detonate if not destroyed.
